    "description": "Claude Code plus Seedance 2.0 on @higgsfield.ai - the most powerful AI duo in the world.\n\nAnd they’ve officially got out of control.\n\nI watched it happen in real time.\n\nSeedance 2.0 is the number one ranked AI video model in the world.\n\nClaude Code runs the entire thing - strategy, copy, competitor analysis, image creation, video production\n\nFully autonomous from one prompt.\n\nHere’s what’s actually happening. You tell Claude to open Higgsfield in your browser.\n\nIt connects through Playwright MCP and controls everything.\n\nWrites the prompt, produces the video, manages full campaigns. From a single instruction.\n\nThis is vibe marketing.\n\nYou describe what you need, the system builds it.\n\nOne prompt. An entire campaign comes back finished.\n\nComment “Claude” and I’ll send you the full setup.\n#claude #claudeai #higgsfield #seedance #aitools",
